Now we will apply UDE \[\left\{
\begin{aligned}
    & I' = \gamma \mathrm{NeuralNetwork}_{\theta}(t,I) I  -\gamma I,\\
    & \mathcal{R}_t = \mathrm{NeuralNetwork}_{\theta}(t,I),
\end{aligned}
\right.\] to learn effective reproduction number from the data generated by logistic model \[
    \left\{
    \begin{aligned}
        & I' = 0.2\left(1-\frac{I}{30}\right)I,\\
        & \mathcal{R}_t = 3-\frac{I}{15}.
    \end{aligned}
    \right.
\]
For detail on mathematics, one can see - Song P, Xiao Y. Estimating time-varying reproduction number by deep learning techniques[J]. J Appl Anal Comput, 2022, 12(3): 1077-1089.
